                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12638655" author="sms" created="Fri, 10 Oct 2008 21:33:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch, adds a new visitor that translates project( * ) inside nested plans of foreach, cogroup and sort if the project&apos;s input has a schema and if the return type of the project is not a bag.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All unit test cases except TestStreaming pass. TestStreaming passes when run in isolation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12638664" author="alangates" created="Fri, 10 Oct 2008 22:15:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12638674" author="olgan" created="Fri, 10 Oct 2008 23:07:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch committed. thanks, santhosh for contributing and alan for reviewing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
